		<title lang="en">IE6 No More (Upgrade from v1.0.0 to v1.0.2)</title>
		
		<description lang="en">Displays the IE6 No More banner on your forum's index page, to encourage users of Internet Explorer 6 to upgrade to a modern browser. This banner is visible only to IE6 users.</description>
		
		<author-notes lang="en">From http://www.ie6nomore.com, a group of people who want to see IE 6 disappear as soon as possible. To help make that happen, they're encouraging IE 6 users to upgrade to a more modern browser, so they can have a better experience using sites and browsing the web.</author-notes>
		
